com.jdbc.ladder.dao
Interface JLadderDao<T>

Type Parameters:
T -
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractJLadderDao
public interface JLadderDao<T>

The super class of Data Access Objects generated through the Jdbc-Ladder. This class offers utility routines for quickly invoking queries and manipulating persistence objects.

Author:
Deepak Garg
